      "text": "/auth\n    /login\n        POST /                 \n            → Login using email + password, return JWT.\n        POST /otp/send        \n            → Send OTP to email/phone for OTP login.\n        POST /otp/verify      \n            → Verify OTP and log user in, return JWT.\n        GET /google           \n            → Redirect user to Google OAuth login.\n        GET /google/callback  \n            → Handle Google response → create/login user → return JWT.\n        GET /github           \n            → Redirect user to GitHub OAuth login.\n        GET /github/callback  \n            → Handle GitHub response → create/login user → return JWT.\n\n    /signup\n        POST /                \n            → Create new user with email + password.\n        POST /otp/send        \n            → Send OTP to verify email during signup.\n        POST /otp/verify      \n            → Verify signup OTP and activate account.\n\n    /password-reset\n        POST /send-otp        \n            → Send OTP to email for resetting password.\n        POST /verify-otp      \n            → Verify OTP and return short-lived resetToken.\n        POST /confirm         \n            → Use resetToken to set a new password.\n\n    GET /auth/me              \n        → Return logged-in user's info using JWT.\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "/auth\n    /login\n        POST /                 \n            → Login using email + password, return JWT.\n        POST /otp/send        \n            → Send OTP to email/phone for OTP login.\n        POST /otp/verify      \n            → Verify OTP and log user in, return JWT.\n        GET /google           \n            → Redirect user to Google OAuth login.\n        GET /google/callback  \n            → Handle Google response → create/login user → return JWT.\n        GET /github           \n            → Redirect user to GitHub OAuth login.\n        GET /github/callback  \n            → Handle GitHub response → create/login user → return JWT.\n\n    /signup\n        POST /                \n            → Create new user with email + password.\n        POST /otp/send        \n            → Send OTP to verify email during signup.\n        POST /otp/verify      \n            → Verify signup OTP and activate account.\n\n    /password-reset\n        POST /send-otp        \n            → Send OTP to email for resetting password.\n        POST /verify-otp      \n            → Verify OTP and return short-lived resetToken.\n        POST /confirm         \n            → Use resetToken to set a new password.\n\n    GET /auth/me              \n        → Return logged-in user's info using JWT.\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
