      "text": "/rooms\n    POST /create              \n        → Create a new room; current user becomes owner.\n    GET  /my                  \n        → Get all rooms created by the current user.\n    GET  /:roomId             \n        → Fetch room details (name, ownerId, createdAt).\n\n    PUT  /:roomId/rename      \n        → Rename the room.\n    DELETE /:roomId           \n        → Delete the room (owner only).\n\n    POST /:roomId/join        \n        → Verify JWT + allow user to join the room.\n    GET  /:roomId/participants\n        → Return list of active users inside the room.\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "/rooms\n    POST /create              \n        → Create a new room; current user becomes owner.\n    GET  /my                  \n        → Get all rooms created by the current user.\n    GET  /:roomId             \n        → Fetch room details (name, ownerId, createdAt).\n\n    PUT  /:roomId/rename      \n        → Rename the room.\n    DELETE /:roomId           \n        → Delete the room (owner only).\n\n    POST /:roomId/join        \n        → Verify JWT + allow user to join the room.\n    GET  /:roomId/participants\n        → Return list of active users inside the room.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
